<p>

He is most remembered for his 1966 short film, "<link>
Jemima and Johnny</link>", inspired by riots in <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../200/94200.xml">
Notting Hill</link></site>
. It won awards at the <film_festival wordnetid="100517418" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../497/32497.xml">
Venice</link></film_festival>
 and <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.8">
<region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
<administrative_district wordnetid="108491826" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
